Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.00,LOGO2,,0,0,0,,翻譯：懒人 リア 校正：懒人 \N時軸：感冒的渣月 小猪 後期：感冒的渣月 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.00,LOGO1,,0,0,0,,萌月字幕組
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:17.00,LOGO2,,0,0,0,,招募聯繫QQ281118926
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.92,OP,,0,0,0,,look up at the sky\N仰望那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:51.68,OP,,0,0,0,,like a bird without wings\N如鸟儿失去翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:53.92,OP,,0,0,0,,if you want to fly\N如果想要飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:57.10,OP,,0,0,0,,feel your breath release yourself\N就去感觉你的呼吸 释放自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:00:58.90,OP,,0,0,0,,why do you sigh\N你为何叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.68,OP,,0,0,0,,just count your blessings\N不如知足常乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.76,OP,,0,0,0,,every time you try\N每一次做出尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:10.84,OP,,0,0,0,,what some thing believes yourself\N都要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.18,OP,,0,0,0,,my mission is gonna be a tough one\N我的任务将会艰巨无比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:23.98,OP,,0,0,0,,i know it's not a game anymore\N也知道这不再是一场游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:26.88,OP,,0,0,0,,i swear that i'll never fail again\N我发誓将不再失败
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.98,OP,,0,0,0,,cause i don't wanna regret anymore \N因为不想让自己再后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:32.72,OP,,0,0,0,,can you hera i'm calling you\N是否听到我在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:35.44,OP,,0,0,0,,i just wanna feel you\N我只是想要触碰到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:38.04,OP,,0,0,0,,don't forget to remember \N别忘了要记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.08,OP,,0,0,0,,so please remember\N所以请记住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:43.98,OP,,0,0,0,,i hear you air calling me\N我听到你气息的呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:46.78,OP,,0,0,0,,i want you to feel me\N我想让你来触碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.40,OP,,0,0,0,,you know i want to surrender \N你知道我想要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.40,0:01:52.24,OP,,0,0,0,,never surrender \N决不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.08,OP,,0,0,0,,my mission i've got to execute\N我的任务我必须完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:57.88,OP,,0,0,0,,i know it'w not a game anymore\N我知道这已不再是游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:00.66,OP,,0,0,0,,i swera i'll never fail again\N我发誓将不再失败
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.20,OP,,0,0,0,,cause i don't wanna regret anymore \N因为不想让自己再后悔
